### =====================
### ResumeIQ API Tests
### =====================

### 1. Test Server
GET http://localhost:5000/
###

### 2. Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "ann@example.com",
  "password": "ann1234"
}

###

### 3. Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ann@example.com",
  "password": "ann1234"
}

###

### 4. Upload Resume (change file path to your actual resume)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/resume/upload
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0QGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc0MTU3OTE3LCJleHAiOjE3NzQyNDQzMTd9.T7Rg4_ef34BpCotZteaDMzuHNwzc9ZcF2VJayG0JgAA
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="ANN_MERIN_SHAJI_RESUME.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< c:\Users\my pc\OneDrive\Documents\ANN_MERIN_SHAJI_RESUME.pdf
------FormBoundary--

###

